---
title: Middle Eastern-Spiced Salmon Bulgur Bowls with Lemon-Garlic Dressing
description: No need for a pita with this tasty bowl! Juicy salmon fillets are tossed in Middle Eastern-style spices and rested atop tender bulgur. Sweet roasted veggies and a DIY lemon-garlic dressing bring it all together.
